result.name: Erawan Thai Premium

reviews.text: The environment is quite nice. And they provided semi buffet lunch during lunch time, and the cheapest one is only $80. The semi buffet offers appetizers like spring roll, crab cake, Tom yum soup, salad, Thai desserts etc. I tried the Thai noodle as main, which is quite good. And my friend s chicken curry is so tasty. In general, the food is quite ok but a bit crowded.

Style over substance. Coconut chicken soup was thin and tasteless. Bit suspicious the chicken soup mostly came out a can. The chicken in the soup and red curry had unpleasant taste. Poorly prepared, tasted like meat was precooked, and just reheated in the curry/soup. Red curry had no spice flavor at all, no aroma/ fragrance. Pad Thai, tasteless, none of the tamarind flavor comes through. Stir fried cabbage was missed off order, but cancelled it on the back of previous dishes. Won't be returning.
Good place for a relaxing lunch on Saturday. Too bad couldn't use the outdoor area. Food is fine.
Nice service and nice good food. Food is pricey
The food is delicious but I suspected that they put Msg in the food cos I had headache and felt very thirsty when I headed back home.

reviews.text: 環境舒適開揚，比起午餐，下午茶很優惠，味道不錯。值得一試

The environment is quite nice. And they provided semi buffet lunch during lunch time, and the cheapest one is only $80. The semi buffet offers appetizers like spring roll, crab cake, Tom yum soup, salad, Thai desserts etc. I tried the Thai noodle as main, which is quite good. And my friend s chicken curry is so tasty. In general, the food is quite ok but a bit crowded.

Gd thai cousin , nice dong yam soup。

自助沙律吧都幾足料豐富，價格偏高但合理的好。 冬陰 足料，夠蝦味又有合適辣度。
但主餐phai Thai 份量偏少， 蝦球都足秤。
咖哩飯都不錯。

冬蔭公湯河，夠足料，湯味好，料夠新鮮。

Style over substance. Coconut chicken soup was thin and tasteless. Bit suspicious the chicken soup mostly came out a can. The chicken in the soup and red curry had unpleasant taste. Poorly prepared, tasted like meat was precooked, and just reheated in the curry/soup. Red curry had no spice flavor at all, no aroma/ fragrance. Pad Thai, tasteless, none of the tamarind flavor comes through. Stir fried cabbage was missed off order, but cancelled it on the back of previous dishes. Won't be returning.

份量十足～合費合理～
店員服務又好又有禮貌～
👍🏽
